## 요약

| 도메인 | 테이블 수 | 저장소 |
|--------|-----------|--------|
| User | users, user_profiles, user_profile_images | MySQL (`maum`) |
| Call | call_sessions | MySQL (`maum`) + Redis (매칭큐) |
| Follow | follows, blocks | MySQL (`maum`) |
| Moment | posts, post_media, comments, post_likes | MySQL (`moment`) |
| Chat | chat_rooms | MySQL (`chat`) + DynamoDB (messages) + Redis (unread) |
| Notification | notifications, notification_settings | MySQL (`notification`) |

